    {
      "id": "fde67bdf-99e8-4bdd-92e2-ed159610af9d",
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "Knowledge tracing is a core component of any intelligent educational system. The way knowledge tracing is modelled involves mapping the learner’s knowledge state against the knwoledge requirements of an exercise.",
